ID.Description: This is a unique identifying number for the pair of AIS transmissions described by the following data.

MMSI_1.Description: This is the Maritime Mobile Service Identity of the first vessel.

BaseDateTime_1.Description: This is the time of the first vessel's AIS transmission.

LAT_1.Description: This is the latitude of the first vessel.

LON_1.Description: This is the longitude of the first vessel.

SOG_1.Description: This is the speed over ground for the first vessel.

COG_1.Description: This is the course over ground for the first vessel.

Heading_1.Description: This is the heading of the first vessel.

VesselName_1.Description: This is the name of the first vessel.

IMO_1.Description: This is the IMO number of the first vessel.

CallSign_1.Description: This is the call sign of the first vessel.

VesselType_1.Description: This is the vessel type for the first vessel.

Status_1.Description: This is the status of the first vessel.

Length_1.Description: This is the length of the first vessel.

Width_1.Description: This is the width of the first vessel.

Draft_1.Description: This is the draft of the first vessel.

Cargo_1.Description: This is the cargo code of the first vessel.

MMSI_2.Description: This is the Maritime Mobile Service Identity of the second vessel.

BaseDateTime_2.Description: This is the time of the second vessel's AIS transmission.

LAT_2.Description: This is the latitude of the second vessel.

LON_2.Description: This is the longitude of the second vessel.

SOG_2.Description: This is the speed over ground for the second vessel.

COG_2.Description: This is the course over ground for the second vessel.

Heading_2.Description: This is the heading of second vessel.

VesselName_2.Description: This is the name of the second vessel.

IMO_2.Description: This is the second vessel's IMO number.

CallSign_2.Description: This is the second vessel's call sign.

VesselType_2.Description: This is the second vessel's vessel type.

Status_2.Description: This is the second vessel's status.

Length_2.Description: This is the second vessel's length.

Width_2.Description: This is the second vessel's width.

Draft_2.Description: This is the second vessel's draft.

Cargo_2.Description: This is the second vessel's cargo code.
